oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Heart Full Of Love (For A Handful Of Kisses) - Bailes Brothers performance - KWKH
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of Heart Full Of Love (For A Handful Of Kisses), written by Eddy Arnold, Steve Nelson, and Ray Soehnel, and performed by the Bailes Brothers with Johnnie Bailes as the lead vocalist. Performance was most likely on The Bailes Brothers and the West Virginia Homefolks radio program on KWKH (Shreveport, La.).
